Module count

Package count.io

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    CountXML
    Defines the XML tags and attributes used in Count
    ExportableData
    Interface for anything that can be written into a data file.
    Removable
    Interface for anything that can be removed.
    SavableData<T>
    A saveable (savable) item has a default file for saving the data.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CommandLine
    Common initialization of problem instance from the command line.
    DataFile<DATA>
    A class for storing different types of Objects (data) with an associated file.
    GeneralizedFileReader
    Common interface to reading files and URLs, possibly compressed.
    ModelBundle
    Hierarchy data structure for storing a session's members: phylogenies, rate models, and profile tables.
    NewickParser
    Newick-format phylogeny parsing.
    RateVariationParser
    Static methods for reading and writing rate variation models.
    TableParser
    Parsing and writing methods for copy-number table data (stored as tab-delimited text).
